import React, { useEffect, useState } from "react";
import LoadingBar from "../LoadingBar/LoadingBar";
import {
  Isprobaj,
  IsprobajResults,
  IsprobajWrapper,
  LoadingBarTitle,
} from "./IsprobajElements";

function Test() {
  const [barPercentage, setbarPercentage] = useState(2000);

  return (
    <Isprobaj>
      <IsprobajInput>test</IsprobajInput>
      <IsprobajResults>
        <IsprobajWrapper>
          <LoadingBarTitle>Temperature</LoadingBarTitle>
          <LoadingBar
            min_progress="0"
            max_progress="6000"
            title="Temperature"
            done={barPercentage}
          />
        </IsprobajWrapper>
        <IsprobajWrapper>
          <LoadingBarTitle>Temperature</LoadingBarTitle>
          <LoadingBar
            min_progress="0"
            max_progress="6000"
            title="Temperature"
            done={barPercentage}
          />
        </IsprobajWrapper>
        <IsprobajWrapper>
          <LoadingBarTitle>Temperature</LoadingBarTitle>
          <LoadingBar
            min_progress="0"
            max_progress="6000"
            title="Temperature"
            done={barPercentage}
          />
        </IsprobajWrapper>
        <IsprobajWrapper>
          <LoadingBarTitle>Temperature</LoadingBarTitle>
          <LoadingBar
            min_progress="0"
            max_progress="6000"
            title="Temperature"
            done={barPercentage}
          />
        </IsprobajWrapper>
      </IsprobajResults>
    </Isprobaj>
  );
}

export default Test;
